Steps connect Spring MVC with Database using Hibernate

1. Create new Maven Project --> Maven Archetype Webapp

2. Add dependencies and plugins
 + maven-war-plugin
 + JSP, JSTL, Servlet
 + web-mvc
 + hibernate-validator
 + java-annotation-api

3. Add hibernate needed dependencies
Require:
 + session factory, session, transaction
 ==> Add dependencies
   + hibernate core
   + spring orm --> ORM mapping
   + spring tx  --> @Transactional
   
 + application.properties --> consists connection parameters
   username, passsword, url, driver

 